# ä»¥ä¸‹ã€ã‚ªãƒªã‚¸ãƒŠãƒ«ã®bm25sã®README

<div align="center">

<h1>BM25-Sparseâš¡</h1>

<i>BM25S is an ultrafast implementation of BM25 in pure Python, powered by Scipy sparse matrices</i>

